edu.iu.dsc.tws.tset.env

Class TSetEnvironment

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iu.dsc.tws.tset.env.TSetEnvironment
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BatchTSetEnvironment, StreamingTSetEnvironment

    public abstract class TSetEnvironment
extends java.lang.Object
    Entry point to tset operations. This is a singleton which initializes as BatchTSetEnvironment or StreamingTSetEnvironment
